Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性绝迹于Altair 原本只能坐以待毙的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抓住一线生机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了对Vega的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始计划捕获能够承受Altair生物环境的女性--Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并使其成为孕育我们星球的未来的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此被选出来的其中一名候选者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是贪睡的夏娃 艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她由于时空转移的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直处于假死状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无苏醒的迹像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而如今她已经是二手货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们暂时返回Altair的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然生下了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其留在了Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些都是琐碎之事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她算不上是真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像这样持续地沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沦为只为安抚你的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无翅的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安抚我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可悲啊 出云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无翅蝴蝶的鳞粉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是如梦似幻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 不如干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给漫长的梦境画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你对艾丽西亚动手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么了结这场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Jin潜入机械天使的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能确定出操纵那机体的Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 出云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Vega 蝴蝶有着复活的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那不被允许的爱也将再度复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不·羁·野·兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这样 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放出你心中那疯狂而又不容抗拒的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底地 毫无保留地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快唤醒沉睡于你体内的有关阿波罗和希尔菲的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲就在你心中那触手可及之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那芬芳的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那甜美的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会为你带来非凡的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她那温热的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱将屡获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 你在渴求爱的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想完成禁断的合体对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多地…更多地渴求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咆哮的饥渴野兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 爱的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了平息你心中的饥渴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着只属于你的爱展开旅途吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兽?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云 我想复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是什么能编织Altair未来的Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是沉睡在Vega的创圣的机械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 就给我记住一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不打算相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再发生什么事 到时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定会把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那力量到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克巴尔金·巴德巴艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不许再企图潜入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎 对同学以枪相向的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在里面多反省一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…听说你好像喜欢艾莉西亚 所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艾莉西亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点差异…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看看侧脸...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷漠的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克巴尔金·巴德巴艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是假冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过Neo DEAVA的最终入学考试的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校需要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断绝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶说过她能理解Jin的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他身上虽然有很多谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不像是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能跟他相处得更融洽一点 交谈更多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相理解更多一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 能互相理解多一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想知道的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想询问的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关那个人的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关那个男人的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的眼神有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说原谅那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像弃犬一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 队伍真长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 两个人都一副闷闷不乐的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好 忘了买果汁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 能让我喝一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公…公然猥亵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这不是间接接吻么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间接接吻?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 也让我喝一口你那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡 你真的很渴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么在机库里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让神乐前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我为你的启程饰以鲜花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后只要你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨以你那忽明忽灭的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去照耀创圣的机械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 不管再怎么口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能在众目睽睽之下做出那种不知羞耻的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往水壶里倒些大麦茶吧 大麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢大麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就红茶 乌龙茶 总之什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 那种行为...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回宿舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你下午的课怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杰西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我给裙子的下摆锁缝了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}才初学不久 做得还不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 真够青涩的啊 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin要是能就此融入集体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装得事不关己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人都如饥似渴地想得到爱情的滋润
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看杰西卡不就如饥似渴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…你突然说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把御子乃心灵的地下水脉挖出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是被禁止恋爱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Abductor的战斗一结束不就毫无问题了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前必须先做好预约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说预约?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃多可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这样慢条斯理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准她会被其他人抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 能耽误你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就行动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是挖洞三兄弟的老二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自立心旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让失去理性的你前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上从Mithra上下来 回到出云大人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我把Iron Sea夷为平地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是死了条心 乖乖地把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}第四区Iron Sea受损 周边居民 请立即到指定避难避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 神乐的战斗能力会在急剧上涨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆季绽放 瞬时凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其花之名为神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是站在爱的那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方机体已退离射线攻击范围 随时可开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把臭女人交给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 神乐 奉上你的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和御子乃到底有什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的…那个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那样 就是…有点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 能请你看着那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是现在马上开始也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到与Abductor的战斗结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨试吼一声吧 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱如今不在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要高声呼唤 就能改变一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就能够扭转乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揍的感觉 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭 好想杀死那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死她…将她拥入怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那力量究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影 是你这家伙干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是 神乐的野性的蒙召
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 出发吧 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着爱的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------ED part1----------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天看过的电影 那就是我们的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.90,0:24:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 从那以后我总是飘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 Aquaria舞动于空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------
